<br>
Here's my idea for Bezerk 5, an ability you get at RR5.<br>
Same as Bezerk 4 with same duration and same 8 minute timer, however with Bezerk 5 you can do 26-124% crit damage and you take on a full-body golden particle effect. The 26-124% varience is the only real gain, and when you think about it that's still just 75% crit on avg. There's also the added 'penalty' of becoming a huge glowing bear that would definately make you a prime target, so that also helps to balance the increased dmg possibility. Even though the glowy effect would technically just be a hindrance, the coolness totally outweighs it. Maybe even add in a red glow on the eyes for that blood thristy enraged look! Give me this and all grievances over 1.62 can be forgiven.<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=mordakain@lighttanksofdaoc>mordakain</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#000000>(8/13/03 1:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=118.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> zerk 5</span><hr size=1> GOOD IDEA! Now go post something on the merc board about giving us some SICK dmg.... got my vote! BRING ZERKERS BACK!<br>
