<br>
Explain to me this, why is it that in DAoC, the berserker works himself into a gigantic whimp who cant parry or evade, and whos only true ability is to transoform into a stupid rat with a blinking &quot;KILL ME!!!&quot; sign above his head??<br>
<br>
First of all, we should have our defensive abilties resotored, i.e., we parry and evade <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>at least</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> at our normal rate.<br>
<br>
Furthermore, I think we should be immune to all CC while frenzied.  You know when you are fighting a mob, try to stun it and get the message something along the lines of &quot;so-and-so is frenzied and blah blah you can't do that...?&quot;  Well we should be like that.<br>
<br>
Make it so, number 1!!<br>
